		(property "Description_1" "Based on the latest enhanced chipset, the new Quectel LC86G series GNSS module supports concurrent reception of GPS, GLONASS, BDS, Galileo and QZSS. The LC86G series is designed to be compatible with Quectel L80 and L86 modules, allowing for smooth migration between them. Compared with single constellation receivers, by enabling multiple GNSS constellations, the LC86G series increases the number of visible satellites, reduces the time to first fix and improves positioning accuracy, especially when driving through dense urban canyons."
